OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774807892
OL,3,CDesigner watch thief caught after
OL,4,Cbeing spotted in bright neon T-shirt
OL,6,FA bungling watch burglar who was
OL,7,Fcaught after being spotted wearing a
OL,8,Fdistinctive neon T-shirt while eating
OL,9,Fin a chip shop has been jailed.
OL,11,FJames Wall stole Gucci and Cartier
OL,12,Fwatches, a diamond ring and a quantity
OL,13,Fof foreign currency during a burglary
OL,14,Fat a home in Southborough, Tunbridge
OL,15,FWells.
OL,17,FThe 20-year-old was driven away from
OL,18,Fthe scene in a silver Vauxhall
OL,19,FInsignia.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
