PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774807892
OL,3,CDesigner watch thief caught after
OL,4,Cbeing spotted in bright neon T-shirt
OL,6,FWithin an hour, patrols spotted the
OL,7,Fvehicle between Junctions 3 and 2 of
OL,8,Fthe M25, anticlockwise.
OL,10,FThe car was seen to be driven
OL,11,Fdangerously, reaching speeds of almost
OL,12,F100mph along the hard shoulder, before
OL,13,Fit was brought to a stop near a slip
OL,14,Froad on the A2 near Wilmington,.
OL,16,FKent Police said the driver had
OL,17,Fattempted to travel the wrong way on
OL,18,Fthe carriageway.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
