OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774807892
OL,3,CDesigner watch thief caught after
OL,4,Cbeing spotted in bright neon T-shirt
OL,6,FA 38-year-old man was arrested at the
OL,7,Fscene in connection with driving
OL,8,Foffences.
OL,10,FHe has been released pending further
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,FA dog handler was deployed to locate
OL,14,FWall, who was recognised due to his
OL,15,Fneon-coloured T-shirt.
OL,17,FHe was arrested inside a chip shop
OL,18,Fnear Bexley, where police found him
OL,19,Feating a portion of fish and chips
OL,20,Fwhile waiting for staff behind the
OL,21,Fcounter to charge his phone.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
