OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774807892
OL,3,CDesigner watch thief caught after
OL,4,Cbeing spotted in bright neon T-shirt
OL,6,FThe device was seized and digital
OL,7,Fforensic analysis placed Wall at the
OL,8,Fscene of the burglary, the force added.
OL,10,FOfficers from the roads policing unit
OL,11,Fhad found two jewellery boxes, two
OL,12,Ffalse vehicle registration plates and
OL,13,Fa jewellery cleaning cloth inside the
OL,14,Fabandoned car.<
OL,16,FWall, of Beverston Gardens in Bristol,
OL,17,FSomerset, pleaded guilty to burglary
OL,18,Fat Maidstone Crown Court and was
OL,19,Fsentenced to two years' in prison.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
