PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774807892
OL,3,CDesigner watch thief caught after
OL,4,Cbeing spotted in bright neon T-shirt
OL,6,FDetective Constable Celia King said:
OL,7,F"Despite being confronted with a
OL,8,Fplethora of evidence proving he was
OL,9,Fresponsible for the burglary, Wall
OL,10,Finitially refused to accept liability
OL,11,Fand laughed while watching footage
OL,12,Ffrom the pursuit.
OL,14,F"The judge took into consideration the
OL,15,Fhigh levels of planning involved in
OL,16,Fthe burglary and as a result, Wall was
OL,17,Fhanded an immediate custodial
OL,18,Fsentence."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
